("13872","640","_crb_about_sections|crb_about_banner_text|0|0|value","“AI will change the world! But how will it change ‘my’ world?” We can help you determine that."),
("13873","640","_crb_about_sections|crb_about_image|0|0|value","http://projects.lollypop.design/navikenz-wp/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/banner.png"),
("13874","640","_crb_about_sections|crb_int_banner_text|1|0|value","“95% of what AI can do in the enterprise is currently not known. We can help you find and implement those unknowns”"),
("13875","640","_crb_about_sections|crb_int_para_text|1|0|value","AI will not be like an ERP Implementation or even a Dot Com implementation like in the earlier decades. It will be like a TQM or a Quality Circle implementation where there is a process of continuous exploration and implementation. This will require a ‘slow burn’ of continuous discovery and solutioning. Organizations need cross functional consulting, architecture and implementation skills in smaller amounts over longer periods of time. With our ‘pod’ structure of delivery, we have pioneered this for the new AI age."),
("13876","640","_crb_about_sections|crb_int_image|1|0|value","http://projects.lollypop.design/navikenz-wp/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/help.png"),
