("14095","655","_crb_careers|crb_careers_cultur_section_boxs:meta_careers_cultur_section_item|5:1|0|value","<h6 class=\"fnt-20 clr-0e\">We have a dynamic work environment where you can make a difference</h6>\r\n<ul class=\"culturAssets__cards__item__innerList\">\r\n 	<li class=\"fnt-20 clr-0e o-8\">Culture of belonging and innovation- We empower Kenziens to take decisions and learn from their experiences to grow as better professionals</li>\r\n 	<li class=\"fnt-20 clr-0e o-8\">We enjoy each other’s company, as we go about solving our customers’ problems, adding value to them, Navikenz and each one of us, the Kenziens</li>\r\n 	<li class=\"fnt-20 clr-0e o-8\">At Navikenz, we enjoy an environment of trust, mutual respect and open communication across the organisation</li>\r\n</ul>"),
