("14099","655","_crb_careers|crb_careers_cultur_section_boxs_2:meta_careers_cultur_section_item_2|5:1|0|value","<h6 class=\"fnt-20 clr-0e\">We provide an ecosystem where we Evolve everyday</h6>\r\n<ul class=\"culturAssets__cards__item__innerList\">\r\n 	<li class=\"fnt-20 clr-0e o-8\">We encourage and facilitate learning and certification at all levels</li>\r\n 	<li class=\"fnt-20 clr-0e o-8\">We organize weekly learning sessions across the firm, where are all employees participate in learning and sharing</li>\r\n</ul>"),
