("570","1","2022-03-26 02:41:12","2022-03-26 02:41:12","<h6>About Navikenz Consulting </h6>\r\n\r\n<p>Navikenz is a seed-funded start-up in the IT-Consulting and Services space, delivering transformative solutions across Business Transformation, Enterprise Technology Strategy, and Product Engineering domains. We are working with CDOs, CIOs, and CTOs of Fortune 100 companies in US, Europe and India to discover and implement high-performance Artificial Intelligence solutions.</p>\r\n<p>Navikenz differentiates itself and drives impact with a pod-driven approach, comprising teams of domain-led business consultants, enterprise architects, and change management experts who work in collaborative, non-hierarchical teams. We engage at all points of the AI-value chain, from strategic direction setting, roadmaps, technology solutioning, product engineering, and managed services.  </p>\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n<h6>Our values define our culture. At Navikenz, are creating a differentiated workplace where -  </h6>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>there is no hierarchy, employees come together as pods to solve problems </li>\r\n<li>there are virtual first, hybrid ways of working, with an ability to define flexible work schedules  </li>\r\n<li>workplace is open, transparent and encourages healthy debate, and diversity of thoughts </li>\r\n<li>a vacation policy which encourages work-life balance </li>\r\n<li>family and well-being are given the most importance  </li>\r\n<li>there is a focus on learning  </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>As a startup, Navikenz is offering early employees value-added compensation benefits, include a well-structured ESOP program, and industry standard compensation  </p>\r\n<h6>About the Role </h6>\r\n<p>As a Principal, you will assist in the leadership and delivery of engagements. You will build on your experience designing and executing transformation programs. You will collaborate and interface with client stakeholders daily. You will also be involved in branding, thought leadership, and knowledge management efforts to provide value-adding consulting services. You will anchor sales proposal preparation and engagement delivery efforts. </p>\r\n<h6>Responsibilities include: </h6>\r\n<h6>Project Execution </h6>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Leading & driving business pitches and present, creative concepts and new and innovative ideas  </li>\r\n<li>Work with client counterparts to define long-term vision, goals, and strategies for digital and data-led transformations </li>\r\n<li>Translate client requirements into actionable project initiatives with associated metrics </li>\r\n<li>Translate domain-specific best practices, and personal experience to impactful recommendations </li>\r\n<li>Support client organizations throughout all phases of the project beyond the recommendation, including hand-holding implementation, and dealing with business change-management </li>\r\n<li>Ensuring effective communication and high satisfaction levels for the client team </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n\r\n<h6>Sales / Business Development </h6>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Support Navikenz leadership team members in driving proposal development</li>\r\n	<li>Develop client relationships to identify and qualify sales opportunities  </li>\r\n	<li>Lead solution definition for client-specific needs during the opportunity to closure cycle </li>\r\n	<li>Articulate a  point of view in thought leadership media, including papers, webinars, and seminars</li>\r\n</ul>  \r\n\r\n\r\n<h6>People Development </h6>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Mentor and coach team members through formal, and informal feedback opportunities </li>\r\n	<li>Collaborate and share knowledge </li> \r\n	<li>Guiding and developing individual team members with an apprenticeship mindset </li>\r\n	<li>Contribute to consulting practice growth through recruitment, training, and retention </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n\r\n<h6>Domain and practice development:  </h6>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Contribute to the firm\'s domain development initiatives. </li>\r\n	<li>Provide insight and thought leadership in development of IP and assets, development of point-of-view, research or white papers, including differentiated points of view and methodologies</li>\r\n	<li>Support development of marketing collateral, public speaking and publications </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n \r\n<h6>To be successful in this role, you must have </h6>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>At least 8+ years of top-tier consulting experience in BFSI/Lifesciences/Telecom</li>\r\n	<li>Consulting/advisory experience post-MBA (Tier- I B-schools) with Technology consulting practices like Big4s/Accenture Strategy/Infosys consulting/MBB etc. </li>\r\n	<li>Experience in managing transformation programs in the areas of AI-led technology </li>\r\n	<li>Experience in driving large scale transformation Management/program management/change management in at least 3 of the following areas - </li>\r\n	<li>Business Strategy formulation: Business case preparation, Go to Market, cost optimization, cost to serve modeling and improvement, Business IT/Digital strategy & roadmap</li>\r\n	<li>Process reimagination & process optimization, including process mining tools </li>\r\n	<li>Experience in implementing various technology platforms, either from a Business Integrator, Systems Integrator or Client role </li>\r\n	<li>Experience in applying or implementing next-generation supply chain technologies such as AI, cognitive automation, Internet-of-Things (IoT), Blockchain, big data analytics </li>\r\n	<li>Experience in conducting Design thinking led innovation workshops</li>\r\n	<li>Affiliations / Certifications: Industry certifications, publications in industry journals and magazines, knowledge and appreciation of digitalization, emerging technologies </li>\r\n</ul> \r\n<p>Location / Contract models Navikenz is a virtual-first location agnostic company; We have established offices in Noida and Bangalore; However, many of our consultants work in flexible hybrid models which involve periodic travel to base offices or client locations.  Our preference is for a full-time resource who can anchor the team. We will be willing to discuss hybrid / part-time / flexi-working arrangements that are mutually beneficial.  \r\n</p>\r\n","Principle Consultant","","publish","closed","closed","","principle-consultant","","","2022-03-26 02:41:12","2022-03-26 02:41:12","","0","http://projects.lollypop.design/navikenz-wp/?post_type=opportunities&#038;p=570","0","opportunities","","0"),
