("631","1","2022-03-28 06:32:46","2022-03-28 06:32:46","<p>We help customers with the development of their AI solutions with capabilities to analyse and classify information with relevant image processing and computer vision tools. The solutions will help process, detect and recognize a variety of real-life objects with speed and high accuracy to accelerate business operations. \r\n</p>\r\n<p>We build solutions that are well adapted to specific industry needs and are able to respond to our customer’s unique business requirements. Our solutions are designed and built to scale and will support emergent business use cases\r\n</p>\r\n<p>Our solutions are based on deep mathematical and statistical foundations leveraging Computer vision and image processing techniques to process, detect and recognize real-life objects to provide business users relevant information for their actions and decisions. \r\n<p>","Image Recognition based AI Solution development","","inherit","closed","closed","","313-revision-v1","","","2022-03-28 06:32:46","2022-03-28 06:32:46","","313","http://projects.lollypop.design/navikenz-wp/?p=631","0","revision","","0"),
("632","1","2022-03-28 06:33:19","2022-03-28 06:33:19","<p>We bring a metrics-based assessment framework to help our customers select the right AI Platform for their business solution needs. The right AI Platform further helps you accelerate the engineering and implementation of AI solutions within your organization and provides the right tools for your Data Scientists, Data Engineers, and the Infrastructure managers.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>We will implement the AI platform for your enterprise to further develop and deploy relevant high-performance AI solutions with the right development tools. We will also train and equip the users in the organization with relevant skills to further maintain, operate and enhance the solutions to ensure they remain aligned to evolving business needs.\r\n</p>","Implement AI Platform for enterprise AI solutions","","inherit","closed","closed","","315-revision-v1","","","2022-03-28 06:33:19","2022-03-28 06:33:19","","315","http://projects.lollypop.design/navikenz-wp/?p=632","0","revision","","0"),
("633","1","2022-03-28 06:33:58","2022-03-28 06:33:58","<p>We help customers with the development of their AI solutions participating all the way from the project planning and data collection phase to designing and training the Machine Learning models. </p>\r\n\r\n<p>We build solutions that are well adapted to specific industry needs and are able to respond to our customer’s unique business requirements. Our solutions are designed and built to scale and will support emergent business use cases</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our solutions are based on deep mathematical and statistical foundations leveraging Machine Learning (ML) techniques to interpret complex data, identify relevant patterns and spot trends to bring you high performance decision support solutions.</p>","Machine Learning (ML) based AI Solution development","","inherit","closed","closed","","309-revision-v1","","","2022-03-28 06:33:58","2022-03-28 06:33:58","","309","http://projects.lollypop.design/navikenz-wp/?p=633","0","revision","","0"),
